{"title":"被遗忘的运算符(??)","date":"2010-07-20T09:41:34.000Z","slug":"被遗忘的运算符","updated":"2019-05-07T09:19:49.772Z","content":"<p>今天发看到一个条件判断</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight csharp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span>( <span class=\"keyword\">value</span> = ( config ?? <span class=\"string\">\"\"</span> ) )</span><br><span class=\"line\">    config ?? <span class=\"string\">\"\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>等同于</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight csharp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">config=<span class=\"literal\">null</span>?<span class=\"string\">\"\"</span>:config;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>意思是如果config为null那么就赋值””否则保持原值不变</p>\n<p>举个例子：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight csharp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span>? i;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> x=i??<span class=\"number\">5</span>;<span class=\"comment\">// 如果i值为null那么给x赋值5，否则x值等于i的值</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>这个运算符只支持引用类型和Nullable类型。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"【花语】-菖蒲","slug":"cloves-changpu"},"next":{"title":"【花语】-狗尾巴草","slug":"cloves-gouweiba"},"link":"http://ojdev.github.io/post/被遗忘的运算符/"}